check boxes, if you can pop it

00:53:03.250 --> 00:53:07.130
over, like drop it down from
the top, or put it in the

00:53:07.130 --> 00:53:10.000
bottom so that you can
see the results.

00:53:10.000 --> 00:53:10.490
RETO MEIER: Absolutely.

